<h2><b>Come join our <a href="https://deviantart.com/users/outgoing?https://discord.gg/vS4TY2Y"><b>Discord Chat</b></a>!</b></h2>
Turfside, created by foxbourne, is a sim game centered around the sport of Thoroughbred flat racing. This group is designed to revolutionize the racing experience on DeviantArt and allow anyone in the community to play without the need for art, literature, or money. Everyone is welcome to participate - see the links above for more information.

